| comment "Dragnet [Ransomware]: dragnet-ransomware-2023-0471 — Recovery Inhibition (clop)"
| comment "Status: experimental | Level: high | ID: 9f9c0b7b-6a29-5e9d-b8fc-a62b66a583a9"
index=* sourcetype=endpoint*
